    "@id": "https://api.nuget.org/v3/catalog0/data/2024.07.09.13.29.47/oidcproxy.net.4.0.0.json#deprecation",
    "message": "Version 4.0.0 keeps caches the JWKS endpoint too long. Consequently, when the keys are rotated, during a window of one hour at max, all newly issued access tokens will be considered invalid. \nThe token signature verification is not waterproof in version 4.0.0. This is problematic when the BFF is not configured to forward requests to downstream APIs but to process request directly.",
    "reasons": [
      "CriticalBugs"
    ]
  },
  "description": "An extendible framework for .NET to implement the BFF Security Pattern (a.k.a. Token Handler Pattern) in Single Page Applications.",
